LEVEL 20 TALENT

Talent 1
increase Volcanus life regeneration by 4 and his mana by 12%
Volcanus will gain 20% of his max mana as health bonus and increasing his mana by 700% of his Mana regeneration

Talent 2
Increase Volcanus attack damage by 10 and his spell amp by 7%
Volcanus spells will gain 15% of his attack damage as Spell damage bonus to them, and increase SpellAmp by 4% of Agility and Strenght

PASSIVE D OR F Fire God
Increase overall stats and give a positive and negative buff

BUFF Volcanus attack will do magic damage instead of physical and he gain 1% spellamp per 7 int instead of 10 and he can use 2 glove
Intead of 1 he also gain 2 life per inteillgence point any damage per second spell will only have 20% duration on Volcanus,
he can also use Sulfuras, getting even more power from it
DEBUFF Volcanus will take 50% more damage from pure,physical and magic damage and he cannot use any weapons but glove as weapons
he also lose 50% base attack damage and all Source of Physical damage will deal 1.5% of Volcanus life as damage bonus to him and
magical Source of damage will do 0.4% bonus damage as well
BONUS BUFF Elemental Gods
When Enigma, Zet and Volcanus are in the same game they gain bonus, gaining 7% spellamp with 5 health regeneration, 10% magic resist,
35 Movespeed FLAT and making their spell that deal damage VS NON-ELEMENTAL BEING 25% more damage but reducing their damage VS ELEMENTAL
BEING by 25%


